@startuml

actor User
participant Gateway
participant WorkerQueue
participant Metrics
participant HPA

User -> Gateway: Increased traffic
Gateway -> WorkerQueue: Requests accumulate
WorkerQueue -> Metrics: Queue length / latency grows
Metrics -> HPA: Signal (CPU + RPS + latency)
HPA -> Gateway: Scale out (add replicas)
Gateway -> User: Response stabilize
note over Gateway: p95 latency returns to normal

@enduml